{
  "stem": "3085.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We moved into-- I don't remember the exact date, but I think sometime in May, we were forced to move into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I had mentioned, we had one room for the four of us, which was quite a change from the previous location, where, of course, we had a whole house.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the circumstances weren't all that severe, even in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I think we had enough food to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't anything like the Warsaw Ghetto, for instance, that-- where things were a lot more, more terrible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we, we were actually-- as kids, actually, we were-- we didn't go to school, of course, but there was-- we were organized into some organized activities and-- including private tutoring type of thing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had some, some other-- but they-- it, it was made sure that we'll have organized activities for the children for the period that we were there, which was about six weeks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At the end of that period-- and I'm not sure, again, of the exact dates-- we were taken away from the ghetto to a, a-- some kind of a-- an, an-- a gendarmerie camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Basically, it was like-- it was stables for horses, I think, that they kept the gendarmerie in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were-- we had to stay in that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Also, it was in Pecs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was a lot-- the conditions were a lot more severe in those-- in, in, in that camp, or gendarmerie camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't honestly recall how my mother got food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had some money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were allowed to, I believe, take some money with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could buy, presumably, food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I, I presume there was still some kind of commerce between the ghetto and the outside world.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
